
---

## **How to Add to GitHub**
1. Create the folder **`gpa-calculator`**.
2. Save **`gpa_calculator.py`** and **`README.md`** in it.
3. Take a screenshot of your running app and save it as **`screenshot.png`** in the same folder.
4. Run these commands:
```bash
cd gpa-calculator
git init
git add .
git commit -m "Initial commit - GPA Calculator"
git branch -M main
git remote add origin https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/gpa-calculator.git
git push -u origin main
